<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN"
"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <title>RED Digital Cinem</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: 'Lucida Grande',Geneva,Arial,Verdana,sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #FFF; background:#000;" >
    <!-- div#wrapper begin -->
    <div id="wrapper" style="width:96%;margin:0 auto;min-width:650px;">
      <!-- #header begin -->
      <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#000" background="http://www.red.com/images/mailer/prepare_delivery/head02.png">
        <tr background="http://www.red.com/images/mailer/prepare_delivery/head02.png">
          <td align='left'><img src="http://www.red.com/images/mailer/prepare_delivery/head01.png" alt='' /> </td>
          <td align='right'><img src="http://www.red.com/images/mailer/prepare_delivery/head03.png" alt='' /> </td>
        </tr>
      </table><!-- #header end -->
      <!-- div#content begin -->
      <div id="content" style="padding: 10px;" >
        <h3><%= "#{@queue.name} -" %></h3>
        <p>You now have an official RED Camera Serial Number(s): <%= @queue.serial_number %></p>
        <p>As your camera order nears delivery, RED will contact you via email with important information such payment information, delivery options, accessory recommendations, and order summary verification.  For the most up-to-date delivery information (estimated delivery timelines, accessory availability, etc), please see the following thread on REDUSER: <a href='http://www.reduser.net/forum/showthread.php?t=7464' style="color: #FFF;">http://www.reduser.net/forum/showthread.php?t=7464</a> .</p>
        <p>
          <br/>
          Thanks,<br/>
          -RED BOMB SQUAD 
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- div#content end -->
    </div>
    <!-- div#wrapper end -->
  </body>
</html>